choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for today.
Sure, here's an example of a healthy meal plan that could be suitable for you:

Breakfast: Overnight oats with banana and almond butter topping (1 cup rolled oats, 1/2 cup unsweetened almond milk, 1 tablespoon chia seeds, 1 teaspoon honey or maple syrup, sliced bananas, and a dollop of almond butter)
Snack: Apple slices with peanut butter (1 medium apple and 2 tablespoons natural peanut butter)
Lunch: Grilled chicken breast salad with mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, cucumbers, avocado, and a drizzle of olive oil and lemon juice dressing.
Snack: Greek yogurt with berries (1 cup plain Greek yogurt topped with 1/2 cup fresh or frozen mixed berries)
Dinner: Baked salmon fillet with roasted vegetables (broccoli, carrots, and sweet potato), served with a side of quinoa.
Snack: Carrot sticks with hummus (1 medium carrot stick and 2 tablespoons hummus)
